<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.6.1">
<l>amparamum perunilaṉun ticaika ḷeṭṭu malaikaṭaluṅ kulavaraiyu muṇṭa kaṇṭaṉ</l>
<l>kompamarum vaṭamaratti ṉilaimēl paḷḷi kūṭiṉāṉti ruvaṭiyē kūṭa kiṟpīr</l>
<l>vampaviḻañ ceṇpakattiṉ vāca muṇṭu maṇivaṇṭu vakuḷattiṉ malarmēl vaiku</l>
<l>cempiyaṉkōc ceṅkaṇāṉ cērnta kōyil tirunaṟaiyūr maṇimāṭañ cērmiṉ kaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are able to join the blessed feet of him who sleeps</l>
<l rend="indent">on the banyan tree leaf which rests on a branch,</l>
<l>The one whose throat consumed the heavens, the great earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">eight directions, roiling seas, and mountain ranges,</l>
<l>Gather at the beautiful raised shrine in Tirunaṟaiyūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">the temple where Cempiyaṉ King Ceṅkaṇāṉ came,</l>
<l>Where jewel[-like] bees rest on blossoms of the bakula tree,</l>
<l rend="indent">having sipped water from champaka [flowers] where fragrance wafts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
